{[#] Also note that Black can often save himself thanks to a piece sacrifice
in the endgame as in the following example:} 27... Bc8 ({To the same would
have led:} 27... d5 28. Bc7 e4 29. b6 Bc8 30. Na5 Na6 31. Bxa6 Bxa6 32. b7 Bc5+
33. Kh1 Bxb7 34. Nxb7 Ba7 $11) 28. b6 Nc6 29. Bc4+ Kg7 30. Bc7 Kf6 $1 31. Bd5
Bb7 32. Bxc6 Bxc6 33. Na5 Bd5 34. b7 Bxb7 35. Nxb7 Ke6 $1 36. Na5 d5 37. Kf2 d4
$1 {[%cal Ge6d5]} 38. Nc4 {1/2-1/2 The game is a draw. It's a fortress.} (38.
Nc6 Kd7 39. Bxe5 Kxc6 40. Bxd4 Kd5) (38. Nc4 e4 39. Bf4) 1/2-1/2

