{[#] The optimal endgame for Black is the one with a knight versus
light-squared bishop:} 39. Qxe4 Qxe4 40. Bxe4 Kf7 41. Kf2 Nxg5 42. Bc2 a3 43.
Ke3 Kf6 44. Kf4 Nf7 45. Bd3 Ne5 46. Bc2 Nd7 {0-1 White resigns.} 0-1

