Qh6 Rg8 49. Rxg8+ Kxg8 50. Qe3 Kf8 51. Kg3 Ke7 52. a4 Qg6+ 53. Kh2 Qf5 54. h4
h5 55. Qe2 Qf4+ 56. Kh3 Qf5+ 57. Kg3 Qg6+ 58. Kf4 Qh6+ 59. Ke4 Qg6+ 60. Kd4 f5
61. Qe3 Qf6+ 62. Kd3 f4 63. Qe4 f3 64. Qh7+ 0-1

